119
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:19,736
Dong Man. Say something!

120
00:09:23,841 --> 00:09:26,176
Why did you touch Sun Ho's laptop?

121
00:09:32,251 --> 00:09:33,346
Dong Man.

122
00:09:34,251 --> 00:09:36,150
