233
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:33,555
I'll do whatever I can...

234
00:18:34,260 --> 00:18:36,855
to stop him from investigating.

235
00:18:37,690 --> 00:18:39,555
I'll get it done this time.

236
00:18:41,301 --> 00:18:43,295
